A cyberpunk-style digital illustration of an infinite recursive tunnel made of translucent neon-blue filing cabinets, each drawer opening to reveal another smaller cabinet inside, spiraling inward toward a glowing core. Holographic document pages float and scatter through the tunnel, some highlighted with pulsing magenta search markers. The scene is set in a dark digital void with circuit board patterns faintly visible in the background. Electric tendrils of data streams connect the nested cabinets like synapses. The perspective draws the eye deep into the recursive spiral, creating a sense of endless depth and digital archaeology. Rain-slicked metallic surfaces reflect the neon glow, and small floating code particles drift through the air like digital dust motes.
